      </textblock>
    </study_pop>
    <sampling_method>Non-Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion criteria:

        Patients diagnosed with Alzheimer's Disease and administered Aricept for the first time.

        Exclusion criteria:

